Package org.skistation.models.DTO

Class TicketSummary

java.lang.Object
org.skistation.models.DTO.TicketSummary
public class TicketSummary extends Object
Represents a summary of a ticket. It contains the active status, total distance, amount of rides left, start time, and end time of the ticket.
